<div class="clearfix"></div>

<div class="container">
	<div>	
		<h2>Automatic Tabs</h2>
		<p>If you have a page like this:</p>
		<pre class="pretty-pre">
		<div>
			<h2>Title 1</h2>
			<div>Content</div>
			<h2>Title 2</h2>
			<div>Content 2</div>
			<h2>Title 3</h2>
			<div>Content 3</div>
			...
		</div>
		</pre>
	<p>Add attributes <code>id="yourUniqueId"</code> and <code>class="tabfy"</code> to the structure container.</p>
		<pre class="pretty-pre">
			<div id="bparticle" class="tabfy">
				...
			</div>
		</pre>
		<div class="well">
			<p>Set attribute <code>data-tab-nav="tab"</code> (default) or <code>data-tab-nav="pill"</code> for the navigation layout.</p>
			<p>Set attribute <code>data-tab-fade="true"</code> to add a fading effect.</p>
		</div>
		<p>This will create a tabbed page.</p>
	</div>
	<div id="bparticle" class="tabfy" data-tab-nav="tab" data-tab-fade="true">		
